{"tid":212481,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"(ptgf)酒店蜜會已婚富豪？傅嘉莉死撐咁啱撞到","createTime":"2017-04-22T12:52:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-23T08:23:08.000Z","uid":49648,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"56ad72da1d0080a902126a619d745d5ff99b38a0","tid":212481,"uid":49648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T12:52:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170422/bkn-20170422163103678-0422_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170422%2Fbkn-20170422163103678-0422_00862_001.html&d=jSYRdVihxMCX8m9Ry8wFHf1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=b20e36ee\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170422/bkn-20170422163103678-0422_00862_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n藝人傅嘉莉（Kelly）出席商場活動，穿上短褲的她露出長腿。提到早前她被影到與已婚富豪莊天龍在峴港的酒店蜜會，Kelly解釋是一場誤會：「張相係我同佢（莊天龍）兩個本人，其實係一個好大嘅誤會，有朋友邀請我去私人活動，撞到佢就say個hi。（你自己獨自去峴港？）係有好多人一齊去，但分唔同時間。（你之前同莊天龍傳緋聞，早前你哋喺峴港又咁啱撞到，會唔會太巧合？）我希望唔好再有類似新聞，希望專注我拍劇工作。（事件太巧合？）我平時有自己嘅社交活動同私人空間，唔想影響工作。（有指全程只係得你同佢兩個人。）好多謝大家關心我，除咗工作之外，我知大家好關心我嘅私事，我想專注工作先，其他不實嘅新聞唔會回應。（你係咪小四？）絕對唔係。（同佢係咩關係？）普通朋友，一直都好少聯絡。（莊天龍係咪畀你朋友邀請出席同一個活動？）可能我哋身邊有唔少common friend，但活動上見唔到佢。我唔知朋友請咗咩人。」<br />\n<br />\n呢d我想要，點先約到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe74cf10ff1333c919cb3be7d93b3d1e1102f13a","tid":212481,"uid":50506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T12:55:38.000Z","msg":"而家係人都知你係臭雞啦<br />\n俾人影到仲扮乜唔係，又話咩專注你拍劇，d戲又屎"},{"pid":"b46f58e5be3fd2b7d22106b5e47dd62effbaed40","tid":212481,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T12:57:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家係人都知你係臭雞啦<br />\n俾人影到仲扮乜唔係，又話咩專注你拍劇，d戲又屎</blockquote><br />\n有錢多好。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"135abee6115e996370fd61ef328b87a13820d15d","tid":212481,"uid":50506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T13:15:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>而家係人都知你係臭雞啦<br />\n俾人影到仲扮乜唔係，又話咩專注你拍劇，d戲又屎</blockquote><br />\n有錢多好。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有錢仲會叫佢依d質素?<br />\n俾d大志好唔好?"},{"pid":"393eeede790527bddb6fc5755eea747331de7b60","tid":212481,"uid":52654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T13:23:48.000Z","msg":"佢短頭髮真係好樣衰"},{"pid":"0507dceb19c7b7eb066df2ec965f16233bc9e210","tid":212481,"uid":1977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T13:26:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢短頭髮真係好樣衰</blockquote><br />\n長同短都醜啦"},{"pid":"0344a41fcf7a352dc91f4d8a3094a8fc11d2638b","tid":212481,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T13:30:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"02e8406813241ebc1173dd768465039d8b5c27c9","tid":212481,"uid":53726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T13:42:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>戇撚鳩<br />\n<br />\n咁coffee都係係殘廁咁既撞到啦</blockquote><br />\ncoffee正好多，<br />\n值得原諒"},{"pid":"1e56f5e6eda22be0bde3b4fdd45f7fdbc8a89cd2","tid":212481,"uid":51512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T16:18:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e84d94be8d6402857838b5d87f03a8ce9d30a71","tid":212481,"uid":55309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T16:51:54.000Z","msg":"宜家903訪問緊佢<br />\n仲話自己鐘意d事業心動ge男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abe4279867066d73a1925a22011dfa563fe19dcc","tid":212481,"uid":55309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T16:52:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>宜家903訪問緊佢<br />\n仲話自己鐘意d事業心重ge男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"4c4858a04bd104daff